---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Case Studies | Real results in mid-sized companies | Lumina Consulting"
  description="Real results: automation, dashboards, and management control in companies across the automotive, real estate, financial, and healthcare sectors in Chile."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-lum-black overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-lum-coral/15 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-lum-coral/10 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
    </div>
    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="badge bg-white/10 text-white border-white/20 mb-6">Real results</span>
        <h1 class="text-white mb-6">Case Studies</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-lum-slate-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Real companies that transformed their operations with data, automation, and intelligence
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case 1: Automotive Network -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-10 scroll-fade">
          <span class="badge-accent mb-4">Case Study</span>
          <h2 class="mb-2">Quality Control Automation and Price Analysis</h2>
          <p class="text-lum-slate">Automotive Dealership Network</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          <!-- Challenge -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">The Challenge</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              An automotive dealership network published dozens of vehicles daily but had no way to detect incomplete listings or compare their prices with the market.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Solution -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">My Solution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              Automated system that scans listings, detects errors, compares prices with competitors, and sends daily reports via email.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Results -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-success/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Results</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-lum-slate text-sm space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                300+ vehicles monitored daily vs. manual review
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Automatic report at 7 AM: from 3 hours of manual work to 0
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Immediate detection of listing errors and off-market prices
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial -->
        <div class="testimonial-card scroll-fade animation-delay-300">
          <p class="text-lg text-lum-slate mb-4">
            "Before, we had to review everything by hand, and errors still slipped through. Now every morning we receive a summary with cars missing photos, prices that are off-market, and clear recommendations. It's like having an analyst working 24/7 for us."
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-lum-black">
            - Commercial Manager, Automotive Dealership Network
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider-gradient" />

  <!-- Case 2: Veterinary Clinic -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-10 scroll-fade">
          <span class="badge-accent mb-4">Case Study</span>
          <h2 class="mb-2">Financial and Operational Visibility</h2>
          <p class="text-lum-slate">Veterinary Clinic Network</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          <!-- Challenge -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">The Challenge</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              An expanding veterinary clinic had no clear view of financial performance. Information was scattered across multiple files with no strategic reporting.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Solution -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">My Solution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              Automated system that extracts data from their management system, processes it with Power Query, and generates visual reports with clear performance visibility.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Results -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-success/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Results</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-lum-slate text-sm space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                From manual Excel exports to a real-time updated dashboard
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Full visibility by section: revenue, procedures, trends
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Management runs from the dashboard: they barely need to log into the ERP anymore
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial -->
        <div class="testimonial-card scroll-fade animation-delay-300">
          <p class="text-lg text-lum-slate mb-4">
            "We had the data, but not the complete picture. Now we can see how each section of the clinic is performing, how much we're generating, and which areas need improvement. It gave us the professionalism boost we needed to grow."
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-lum-black">
            - Director, Veterinary Clinic Network
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider-gradient" />

  <!-- Case 3: Real Estate Holding -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-10 scroll-fade">
          <span class="badge-accent mb-4">Case Study</span>
          <h2 class="mb-2">Complete Financial Visibility for Short-Term Rentals</h2>
          <p class="text-lum-slate">Real Estate Holding</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          <!-- Challenge -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">The Challenge</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              The partners couldn't see the real profitability of their short-term rental apartments. Data was scattered across the booking platform, accounting, and external variables like UF and dollar exchange rates.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Solution -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">My Solution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              We integrated Cloudbeds (bookings), Softland (accounting), and UF/dollar data from the CMF into a single Power BI dashboard. Revenue per room, booking lead time, guest origin, and live income statements.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Results -->
          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-success/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Results</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-lum-slate text-sm space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                3 data sources integrated: bookings + accounting + financial indicators
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Per-unit profitability visible in real time
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Actual vs. projected cash flow: partners informed without depending on the accountant
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial -->
        <div class="testimonial-card scroll-fade animation-delay-300">
          <p class="text-lg text-lum-slate mb-4">
            "We went from an accounting black box to having total visibility of the business. Today we see revenue per room, booking lead time, guest origin, live income statements, and actual vs. projected cash flow, all in one place."
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-lum-black">
            - Partner, Real Estate Holding
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider-gradient" />

  <!-- Case 4: Financial Group -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-10 scroll-fade">
          <span class="badge-coral mb-4">Case Study</span>
          <h2 class="mb-2">HR Analytics and Interactive Org Charts</h2>
          <p class="text-lum-slate">Financial Group</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          <div class="card scroll-fade">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-lum-black">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">The Challenge</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              Organization with 4,000+ employees. Org charts were updated manually in PowerPoint (4+ hours). Performance evaluations had undetected biases. Existing software cost USD 15,000/year.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card scroll-fade delay-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-lum-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-lum-black">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">My Solution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              NodalTree: interactive org chart from HR data (Excel/CSV/DB). Automatic updates, drag & drop editing, PDF export. Evaluation calibration system with bias detection.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card scroll-fade delay-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-lum-success/10 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-lum-black">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Results</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-lum-slate text-sm space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Org chart updates in 10 minutes (vs. 4 hours)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Biases identified across 100+ evaluating managers
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Replaced USD 15,000/year software
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider-gradient" />

  <!-- Case 5: Aquaculture LED -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-10 scroll-fade">
          <span class="badge-accent mb-4">Case Study</span>
          <h2 class="mb-2">Document RPA and Regulatory Automation</h2>
          <p class="text-lum-slate">SME in industrial LED lighting for aquaculture</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
          <div class="card scroll-fade">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">The Challenge</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              Regulatory and document processes (permits, certifications, environmental reports) consumed hours of the technical team every day. No consolidated view of active projects nor of upcoming deadlines.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">My Solution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lum-slate text-sm">
              End-to-end document RPA with Playwright + Python on regulatory portals without API. Orchestration in n8n, FastAPI to integrate with internal systems, PostgreSQL for data. Active 24/7 monitoring.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lum-success/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lum-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg">Results</h3>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-lum-slate text-sm space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Processes that took hours, cut down to minutes
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Full traceability of documents per project and due date
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-lum-success flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                System in production with operational SLA, not a pilot
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

